data.value: Hi! I'm Beatriz Varona, I'm an Astrophysicist. I work at the Astronomical Observatory of Teide, of the Instituto de Astrofísica de Canarias. I also worked at the Astronomical Observatory of Cantabria and CHARA Array in California.
